ay by various kinds of strange teachings; for it is good for the heart to be established by grace and not by food regulations, since those who observe them have not benefited. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:14","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 2:16","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 4:14","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"Col 2:16","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:13:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"We have an altar from which those who worship at the tabernacle do not have a right to eat. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:13","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 10:18","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 9:13","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":13},{"label":"1Co 10:18","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:13:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For the bodies of those animals whose blood is brought into the most holy place by the high priest "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:13","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 10:18","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" as a sin offering are burned outside the camp. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 29:14","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 16:27","book":"Lev","chapter":16,"verse":27,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 9:13","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":13},{"label":"1Co 10:18","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":18},{"label":"Ex 29:14","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":14},{"label":"Lv 16:27","book":"Lev","chapter":16,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:13:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, Jesus also suffered outside the gate, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 19:17","book":"Jhn","chapter":19,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:58","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":58,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that he might sanctify "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or set apart, or consecrate"},{"kind":"text","text":" the people by his own blood. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 19:17","book":"Jhn","chapter":19,"verse":17},{"label":"Ac 7:58","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":58}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or set apart, or consecrate"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:13:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Let us, then, go to him outside the camp, bearing his disgrace. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:26","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 4:14","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Heb 11:26","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":26},{"label":"1Pt 4:14","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:13:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For we do not have an enduring city here; instead, we seek the one to come. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mc 3:10","book":"Mic","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 12:22","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mc 3:10","book":"Mic","chapter":3,"verse":10},{"label":"Heb 12:22","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:13:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, through him let us continually offer up to God a sacrifice of praise, that is, the fruit of lips that confess his name. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 7:12","book":"Lev","chapter":7,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 14:2","book":"Hos","chapter":14,"verse":2,"letter":"b"}